description: A mixed use redevelopment. Demolition of existing retail units and construction of part two storey, part single storey building comprising three retail units (Use Class A1 to A5) to land north of railway line. Construction of 11 to 12 storey building to form 79 Self-Contained flats (24 x 1 bed, 55 x 2 bed) to land adjacent to Walthamstow Central station.
site_name: Land Adjacent to South of Walthamstow Central Station
